highlights.text: “come out and play” by Billie Eilish is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 161 spots at #20.
“Say You Won't Let Go” by James Arthur has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 101 weeks straight.
XXXTENTACION has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Arms Around You (feat. Maluma & Swae Lee)” is the highest at #9.
“KIKA” by 6ix9ine and Tory Lanez is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #62.
